title: Zeit Unseen 1/29: Syphilis, Shaun Weiss, Mini Mouse, Top Secret, Old Bay
itunes:title: Zeit Unseen 1/29: Syphilis, Shaun Weiss, Mini Mouse, Top Secret, Old Bay
description:
On this edition of Zeit Unseen Jack and Miles discuss untreated Syphilis, Shaun Weiss getting arrested, a video of Mini Mouse beating someone up, the White House doesn’t want the secrets in John Bolton’s book to reach the public, and Old Bay announces a hot sauce.
